= SDL_GetCPUCacheLineSize =
Use this function to return the L1 cache line size of the CPU.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetCPUCacheLineSize(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns the L1 cache line size of the CPU on success^, or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information^.

